      <bioghist id="aspace_f9c1909ee3d03b514d3c73a7f830258b">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>John Herrick Jackson was born on January 8, 1912, in New Haven, Connecticut.  He graduated from Yale College with a B.A. in 1934.  While at Yale, he participated in several extracurricular activities including Student Council and the Class Book Committee.  He was a member of the Crew team for four years, serving as the team captain in his final year.  He was also a member of Chi Psi, the Torch Honor Society, and Skull and Bones.</p>  
      </bioghist>
